[Unusually dry conditions may lead people to store water in their houses and other buildings, providing breeding sites for _Aedes aegypti_, the mosquito vector of the dengue viruses.

A Map of Central America can be accessed at http://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/camerica.htm#.Udmgx65Vgxc. - Mod.TY]

