[2] Cases in various countries:
The Americas and Central America
---
- The Americas and Central America. 3 Jul 2013. Dengue in the continent total cases reported to WHO 876 859 cases; DHF/serious 8406 cases. Central America countries: health alert in Costa Rica, Nicaragua, deaths 10 (total in both countries); Nicaragua and Honduras dengue virus type 2; Honduras 8000 cases 10 deaths; Costa Rica 12 000 cases 3 deaths.
http://www.telesurtv.net/articulos/2013/07/03/en-alerta-epidemiologica-nicaragua-y-costa-rica-por-aumento-de-casos-de-dengue-3152.html [in Spanish]

